# Health Check Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health

### Generate Temporary Token
POST http://localhost:8000/api/patient/tokens/generate/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expiration_minutes": 30
}

### Access Patient Data via Token (Public)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/patient/token/YOUR_TEMPORARY_TOKEN

### List Active Tokens
GET http://localhost:8000/api/patient/tokens/active
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Revoke Specific Token
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/patient/tokens/revoke/YOUR_TEMPORARY_TOKEN
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Revoke All Tokens
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/patient/tokens/revoke-all
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Login to get access token
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}